.entry-header
Opened in 1966, this eighty-acre community consists of 572 home sites which are mostly occupied by double-section manufactured homes. Amenities here include two swimming pools (one heated), two recreation lounges, shuffleboard courts, Bocce court and a car wash area. Residents also enjoy personalized mailboxes and street lights at every home site. Services provided include city water, city waste water service, separate irrigation water for lawns, garbage and trash removal, lawn mowing and lawn pest control services, basic extended cable TV service, courtesy bus privileges and use of recreational facilities.  Centrally located in Daytona Beach, this community is close to all types of shopping, restaurants, banking and other professional facilities and medical facilities. An active upgrade program here provides an opportunity for new residents to acquire new homes.
